{"tid":2090386,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方搜查筲箕灣黃店「壹碗壹碟」稱連儂牆或違法　店方宣布休業","createTime":"2020-07-02T06:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T07:31:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d254efbdeaed373ff0eba5d4c73604343650a5ef","tid":2090386,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"今早11時許，位於筲箕灣東大街的「壹碗壹碟」，透過facebook宣布休業至另行通知，並留言呼籲「通知所有舖頭拆除文宣」。本報記者到場了解，「壹碗壹碟」已拉下鐵閘，店員忙於清理連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指出，4名軍裝警員早上10時許到達「壹碗壹碟」，向店員稱接獲報案，指有人於店舖內違反《港區國安法》，4名警員到場拍照後，向店員稱店舖停業時屬私人地方可貼文宣，營業時即變成公眾地方，連儂牆有可能違法。據悉，當時警員未有進一步行動便離去，店內兩名店員隨即通知店東，店東對事件感憂心，決定即時清理文宣。"},{"pid":"8611db1c548d22616655e1098c77861cfac0e2e5","tid":2090386,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593668738689/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593668738689%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8CT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=84c5c952\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200702%2Fs00001%2F1593668738689%2F&h=6013475f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200702/s00001/1593668738689/</a>"},{"pid":"6a624cf4fdca6d9841d74595da016ea17a81ef9e","tid":2090386,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:46:23.000Z","msg":"黃店撕文宣？香港人永遠都係創意無限，入黎教你一招破解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18e1df23d2d3227e4c9704c3c9bb6caae02286a2","tid":2090386,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3dd9e46f51ea05856552d007c392bc6da209d0","tid":2090386,"uid":235535,"like":